Package com.ikalagaming.util

Various utility classes that do not fit into other packages.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayOperations
    Methods useful for Arrays.
    BinaryTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    A binary AVL tree for storing (comparable) objects.
    FileUtils
    Contains helper methods for handling files.
    IntegerTree
    A BinaryTree subclass for storing integers.
    NameRegistry
    Contains a list of Strings.
    SafeResourceLoader
    Adds methods for accessing resources.
    StringOperations
    Methods useful for Strings.
    SystemProperties
    Contains methods for fetching various system information such as the Java version or the directory in which applications store data.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicateEntry
    A collision was found when inserting an object into a BinaryTree.
    InvalidOperation
    A collision was found when inserting an object into a BinaryTree.
